  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9a4873f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FUBWAWibiaa4jeMiaicQshgzh1294N71RDkVreHLGuxAHI1MY3S43UmnLDNExovLala23QmtIjEtbQXAxZUJuGLMx7g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span data-eleid=\"3\"><span leaf=\"\">今天，GLM-4.7-Flash正式发布并开源。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span data-eleid=\"3\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.7-Flash是一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">混合思考</span>模型，总参数量为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">30B</span>，激活参数量为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">3B</span>，作为同级别SOTA模型，为轻量化部署提供了一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">兼顾性能与效率</span>的新选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">即日起，GLM-4.7-Fla</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">sh将替代GLM-4.5-Flash，在智谱开放平台BigModel.cn上线，并供<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">免费</span>调用。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">小而强</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">在SWE-bench Verified、τ²-Bench等主流基准测试中，GLM-4.7-Flash的综合表现超过gpt-oss-20b、Qwen3-30B-A3B-Thinking-2507，在相同和近似尺寸模型系列中取得<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">开源SOTA分数</span>。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">在内部的编程实测中，GLM-4.7-Flash在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">前、后端任务</span>上表现出色。在编程场景之外，我们也推荐大家在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">中文写作、翻译、长文本、情感/角色扮演</span>等通用场景中体验GLM-4.7-Flash。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkl3ibl6tk9\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1631599841206828\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"5038\" style=\"display:inline-block;max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;background-color:transparent;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UBWAWibiaa4jeMiaicQshgzh1294N71RDkVr8zNv5MpZ1icSzXfjfu7g5t3t3egItoJ1h5552VvNW0ia6OWmicjphI7BQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"576\" data-cropsely2=\"670\" data-imgfileid=\"100009407\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36b0b543&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUBWAWibiaa4jeMiaicQshgzh1294N71RDkVr8zNv5MpZ1icSzXfjfu7g5t3t3egItoJ1h5552VvNW0ia6OWmicjphI7BQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;text-align: center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">开始使用</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">API接入</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">体验中心：<a href=\"https://bigmodel.cn/trialcenter/modeltrial/text?modelCode=glm-4.7-flash\" target=\"_blank\">https://bigmodel.cn/trialcenter/modeltrial/text?modelCode=glm-4.7-flash</a></span></span></li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">使用指南：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/free/glm-4.7-flash\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/free/glm-4.7-flash</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">接口文档：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/api-reference/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/api-reference/</a></span><span leaf=\"\">模型-api/对话补全</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">上一代免费语言模型GLM-4.5-Flash将于<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">2026年1月30日</span>下线，请您及时将模型编码更新为最新版本。GLM-4.5-Flash正式下线后，相关请求将会自动路由至GLM-4.7-Flash。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">开源部署</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">Hugging Face：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-4.7-Flash\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-4.7-Flash</a></span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">魔搭社区：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.7-Flash\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.7-Flash</a></span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱正式发布并开源 GLM-4.7-Flash 混合思考模型，凭借 3B 激活参数实现同级别 SOTA 性能，并支持 API 免费调用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱正式发布并开源 GLM-4.7-Flash 混合思考模型，凭借 3B 激活参数实现同级别 SOTA 性能，并支持 API 免费调用。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了智谱最新发布的轻量化模型 GLM-4.7-Flash。该模型采用混合思考架构，总参数量为 30B，激活参数量仅为 3B，旨在提供兼顾高性能与高效率的部署方案。在 SWE-bench Verified 等基准测试中，其表现优于同尺寸的 Qwen3 及 GPT 系列模型，尤其在编程、中文写作和长文本处理方面表现出色。目前该模型已在智谱开放平台上线并提供免费 API 调用，同时在 Hugging Face 和魔搭社区同步开源，将全面替代上一代 GLM-4.5-Flash 模型。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GLM-4.7-Flash 采用混合思考架构，实现小参数下的高性能。",
      "explanation": "模型总参数 30B，实际激活仅 3B，通过混合思考机制在保持轻量化的同时，在编程和通用任务上达到了同级别 SOTA 水平。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型全面开源并提供免费 API 服务，降低开发者使用门槛。",
      "explanation": "智谱通过开放平台提供免费调用，并在主流开源社区发布模型权重，旨在推动轻量化模型在端侧和云端的广泛应用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "产品线平滑升级，GLM-4.7-Flash 将替代旧版 Flash 模型。",
      "explanation": "官方明确了升级路径，上一代 GLM-4.5-Flash 将于 2026 年 1 月底下线，新模型将承接所有自动化路由请求。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "GLM-4.7-Flash 是一个混合思考模型，总参数量为 30B，激活参数量为 3B，作为同级别 SOTA 模型，为轻量化部署提供了一个兼顾性能与效率的新选择。",
    "在相同和近似尺寸模型系列中取得开源 SOTA 分数。",
